To install: download the provided .apk file onto an Android device running SKD 21 or higher.

To navigate: swipe back and forth or tap on the tab icons to navigate between the three tabs.
Button effects:
  Heart-shaped button on Recipes: add to favourites
  Screen button on Recipes and Favourites: open recipe in web browser
  Trash can button on Favourites and Ingredients: remove item
  Pencil button on Ingredients: edit ingredient
  
Taskbar:
  Magnifying glass: search in current fragment
  Camera: open barcode scanner
  Menu: open settings
  
No recipes will appear until at least one ingredient is input.
